{"tid":1476864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣妹子撐反送中 IG狂被內地人灌留言","createTime":"2019-08-16T03:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T13:08:05.000Z","uid":10277,"like":335,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"3204ec7e7e3f5236b6e4c0da74d9693448aad3cb","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5VUJCr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5VUJCr.png&h=66a99e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2njUJ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2njUJ7.png&h=2db5a988&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zy7jaO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zy7jaO.png&h=a3417cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢每一個post入面都幾乎有成千個五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係Instagram#反送中Tag都係頭幾位<br />\n我地唔好留言 全部report曬佢地<br />\n冷氣軍師你依家有嘢做啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/geQag2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgeQag2T.png&h=06fba598&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ocpa1uz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcpa1uz.png&h=39b26399&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RtMAs9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRtMAs9z.png&h=8f7d109f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGm8N9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGm8N9A.png&h=75b53ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地鍾意點report都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bd7146c00144dc3c2a0c5c8da45535a0430ff4","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自鞭十連"},{"pid":"73987a3cb93071049d0