\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自鞭十連"},{"pid":"907c059687163b6f3562b8b6cde6a1f01a169d45","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"032466afe82208fb5fe2bca16746903e4a5199d4","tid":1476864,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0c72aad65b233d19dcfc722c588acd77a65e429","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"14ae73fb7f7ba4a899743e0276f90af8b33ce167","tid":1476864,"uid":89558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"全支那究竟有幾多隻五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"好撚多 頭先先鬧走幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和平理性虛心向佢地學習<br />\n問佢地乜係六四"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"問佢地爬牆係咪言論自由嘅一種"},{"pid":"cbd0ebdeb4b2a0eec28f9f6c44a95e2ca92f0020","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:26:57.000Z","msg":"筆名是「狗娃子天一」的中國劉姓「Boys&rsquo; Love」耽美小說作家2017年作品曾在數月內狂銷7000本，今年10月底卻被中國法院一審認定為「淫穢出版物」，判處10年6個月有期徒刑，本月開庭時她邊哭邊疑惑地問道：「是不是我們這些人真正屬於作奸犯科？」<br />\n<br />\n由劉姓作家出品的BL小說《攻占》去年在中國網路文學類中異軍突起，剛上架就襲捲當地網路，但歷經短暫熱銷期後即遭禁售，相關人員也被逮捕，據傳，前後一共賣出約7000本，收入約15萬人民幣（約67.5萬台幣），作者、製作及販賣的相關人員全被判刑，徒刑從10年6個月到10個月不等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國的自由"},{"pid":"9fac68b557d2f82afe18e35031feab8cf587d941","tid":1476864,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"907c059687163b6f3562b8b6cde6a1f01a169d45","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"032466afe82208fb5fe2bca16746903e4a5199d4","tid":1476864,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0c72aad65b233d19dcfc722c588acd77a65e429","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"好撚多 頭先先鬧走幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和平理性虛心向佢地學習<br />\n問佢地乜係六四"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"問佢地爬牆係咪言論自由嘅一種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"剩係up 8964就ok 佢地驚比人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7062727522f76a44bcbfabe0126d0e1ec213ec5","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"網紅「館長」陳之漢曾在直播提到，朋友的哥哥在中國「被領身分證」，今（22）天有人現身說法，表示當時上臉書抱怨有「被強暴」的感受，因此遭中國人留言灌爆、登上微博熱搜，公安還上門找人，嚇得他趕緊回台，一路上心驚膽戰，直到飛機落地才心安。也因為有這樣的經歷，他表示：「我挺香港」、「反送中」、「自由萬歲」。<br />\n<br />\n曾姓網友今（22）天發臉書分享，5月他出差中國考了駕照，卻被要求按壓指紋、拍照，作為大數據資料庫建檔，令他相當不舒服；事後，曾姓網友除了拿駕照，還收到一張「附有大陸公民身分證號」的台灣居民居住證，讓他感覺「被強暴」，發臉書揶揄「怎麼一夜醒來變成中國人」"},{"pid":"56ce40aa1ea816d9151a2704de1ffa95ae088415","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"隔天，公安果然到辦公室索人，威嚇「叫那個台灣人講話小心點」。曾姓網友趕緊買最近一班飛機回台，一路上忐忑不安，過海關時擔心被拘捕，登機後害怕遇上天候不佳，班機返回中國等等。<br />\n<br />\n原PO說，飛機落地那一刻，「我真的激動到差點哭了」，那瞬間強烈意識到「台灣才真的是我的家，這裡才是能真正讓我放心的地方」。事件全程約20個小時，對他而言卻如惡夢一般。<br />\n<br />\n事後，中國官方仍打電話到原PO辦公室關切，甚至有不明人士到他的中國住所尋人。幾天後，6、7百則的微博轉發文全數下架，「這一切都好像沒發生過一般。」<br />\n<br />\n原PO說，雖然不是犯了法律條例的罪，但大家都知道，中國的標準與一般國家不同，「所以我不知道假若香港的送中條例通過了以後，我是不是也去不了了。」<br />\n<br />\n網友們回應，「恭喜你平安歸國」、「還好你平安回來了，太恐怖了，太可怕了」、「不要對中國人有太好的想像，封閉的環境日久，人的思維已經...」、「精神折磨」"},{"pid":"f5b6cb900247e21aee60ca8fbc682978d149ed4a","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QCG8jA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QCG8jA.png&h=166f8b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻......牆"},{"pid":"29e89fbfab34c3934581f6335b391af7fffb72df","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fac68b557d2f82afe18e35031feab8cf587d941","tid":1476864,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"907c059687163b6f3562b8b6cde6a1f01a169d45","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"032466afe82208fb5fe2bca16746903e4a5199d4","tid":1476864,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"問佢地爬牆係咪言論自由嘅一種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"剩係up 8964就ok 佢地驚比人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫佢地百度以下64、六四 公安即刻上門"},{"pid":"d05722bde1fbd94405649bee5e9b6cba9558ab76","tid":1476864,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"818<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79059d1cbf8b68393f4530b5c70f339daa936bdf","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29e89fbfab34c3934581f6335b391af7fffb72df","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fac68b557d2f82afe18e35031feab8cf587d941","tid":1476864,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"907c059687163b6f3562b8b6cde6a1f01a169d45","tid":1476864,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"問佢地爬牆係咪言論自由嘅一種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"剩係up 8964就ok 佢地驚比人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg